        <div type="letter">
            <div type="text">
                <opener>
                    <placeName><hi rend="print">Down, | Beckenham, Kent. | Railway Station | Orpington. S.E.R.</hi></placeName>
                    <date>March 9<hi rend="superscript">th</hi> 1877</date>
                    <salute>My dear Sir</salute>
                </opener>
                <div type="transcription">
                     
<p>I thank you warmly for your letter.—<ref target="#foot.f1"/> I can assure you that I did not require any word from you to be perfectly convinced of your very kind feelings towards me, &amp; of your estimation of what I have been able to do in Science, which is far higher than I deserve.</p>
<p>Believe me Dear Sir | With much respect | Yours very faithfully | Charles Darwin</p> 
                </div>
            </div>

            
            
